Add parental controls and content filtering functionalities.
* **Backend Changes:** - Add endpoints for handling parental controls, content filter, and time restriction settings in `safenet/backend/main.py`. - Add models and schemas for content filter and time restriction in `safenet/backend/models.py` and `safenet/backend/schemas.py`. - Add routes for content filter and time restriction in `safenet/backend/routers/parental_controls.py`. - Add tests for content filter and time restriction functionalities in `safenet/backend/tests/test_parental_controls.py`. - Update requirements in `safenet/backend/requirements.txt`.
* **Authentication Enhancements:** - Add `email` and `full_name` fields to `SignupRequest` in `safenet/backend/routers/auth.py`. - Add forgot password functionality in `safenet/backend/routers/auth.py`. - Add password reset token creation and verification functions in `safenet/backend/security.py`. - Add tests for forgot password functionality in `safenet/backend/tests/test_auth.py`.
* **Frontend Changes:** - Update `SignupForm.tsx` to send `full_name` and `email` fields to the backend. - Update `ForgotPasswordForm.tsx` to handle password reset requests and display success/error messages.
